{"id":10981,"date":"2025-08-03T15:52:45","date_gmt":"2025-08-03T15:52:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/cachesafaris.com\/?post_type=tours&#038;p=10981"},"modified":"2026-05-07T08:53:32","modified_gmt":"2026-05-07T08:53:32","slug":"7-days-best-of-kenya-safari","status":"publish","type":"tours","link":"https:\/\/cachesafaris.com\/tours\/7-days-best-of-kenya-safari\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Days Best of Kenya safari"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Embark on a breathtaking 7-day luxury safari through Kenya\u2019s most iconic landscapes, from the sweeping savannas of the Great Rift Valley to the majestic plains of the <a href=\"https:\/\/cachesafaris.com\/tours\/7-days-masai-mara-nakurunaivasha-and-amboseli-budget-safari\/\" data-type=\"tours\" data-id=\"10522\">Masai Mara. <\/a>This meticulously crafted journey combines thrilling wildlife encounters with stays in premier lodges and tented camps, offering unparalleled comfort and world-class hospitality. Explore Amboseli National Park with Mount Kilimanjaro as your backdrop, witness the awe-inspiring wildebeest migration in the Masai Mara, and discover the serene beauty of Lake Naivasha and <a href=\"https:\/\/cachesafaris.com\/lake-nakuru\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"9969\">Lake Nakuru.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Tour Highlights<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong>Amboseli National Park<\/strong>: Marvel at vast elephant herds and diverse wildlife against the stunning snow-capped Mount Kilimanjaro.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Masai Mara National Reserve<\/strong>: Experience the drama of the Great Migration and track the Big Five in Kenya\u2019s most famous reserve.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Lake Naivasha<\/strong>: Enjoy boat rides and encounters with hippos, zebras, and giraffes at Crescent Island or the dramatic landscapes of Hell\u2019s Gate.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Lake Nakuru National Park<\/strong>: Admire flamingo-lined shores and spot rhinos, 